text: I've lived the promise of America, and I see the promise of America in all of you.
I see it in the young people who are voting for the first time, who are determined to
live free from gun violence and to protect our planet and to shape the world they inherit.
I see it in the women who refuse to accept a future without reproductive freedom.
And the men who support them.
I see it in Republicans who have never voted for a Democrat before, but have put the Constitution
of the United States over party.
